Cedric Yarbrough https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cedric_Yarbrough 0 Cedric Yarbrough (born March 20, 1973) is an American comedian, singer, voice artist and actor. He starred on the Comedy Central television series Reno 911! as Deputy S. Jones and currently stars on the ABC sitcom Speechless, as well as voicing Officer Meow Meow Fuzzyface on the Netflix comedy-drama BoJack Horseman.
